                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On June 3, Secretary of State <persName corresp="#p_DULLESJF1">Dulles</persName>
                    appeared before the Joint Congressional Committee on Atomic Energy to support
                    amendments to the Atomic Energy Act of 1946. <persName corresp="#p_DULLESJF1"
                        >Dulles</persName>’ statement before the Joint Committee was subsequently
                    made public in Department <pb facs="0643" n="1457" xml:id="pg_1457"/> of State
                    Press Release No. 205, June 3, 1954, printed in Department of State <hi
                        rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, June 14, 1954, pages 926–928.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
